  "title": "Guest Service Ambassador | Orchard",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Bugis / Orchard<br>\n⏰ <strong>Shift Hours:</strong> 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM / 3:00 PM – 11:00 PM / 10:00 PM – 7:30 AM (rotating shifts)<br>\n🎁 <strong>Benefits:</strong> Annual Leave, Variable Bonus, 13th-Month Bonus</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Welcome guests with warmth and professionalism during check-in and throughout their stay</li>\n  <li>Manage front desk operations, including check-ins, check-outs, and reservations</li>\n  <li>Respond to guest enquiries and feedback promptly, ensuring a smooth and pleasant experience</li>\n  <li>Maintain and update guest records accurately in the system</li>\n  <li>Liaise with internal departments to ensure all guest needs are addressed efficiently</li>\n  <li>Promote hotel amenities and services to enhance guest satisfaction and encourage repeat visits</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior experience in front office, guest services, or hospitality roles preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills; confident engaging, with guests from all walks of life</li>\n  <li>Resourceful, with a problem-solving mindset and ability to remain calm under pressure</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with hotel management systems is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn — full training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Passion for delivering great service and creating memorable guest interactions</li>\n  <li>Able to work rotating shifts, including overnight, weekends, and public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates please WhatsApp me at 8779 6100 or send in your resume to willie.goh@swiftsearchglobal.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Willie Goh | EA Reg No: R2197853</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Swift Search Global Pte Ltd | EA No: 18C9495</p>",
